Achievements.Name: Everybody Starts Somewhere
Achievements.Description: Buy your first property

Achievements.Name: Now You're On Your Way
Achievements.Description: Own your first monopoly

Achievements.Name: Climbing Your Way Up The Ladder
Achievements.Description: Build your first set of houses.  Classic mode only.

Achievements.Name: The View From The Top
Achievements.Description: Build your first set of hotels. Classic mode only.

Achievements.Name: High Roller
Achievements.Description: Roll a double six

Achievements.Name: Rolled To Jail
Achievements.Description: Roll three doubles in a row and get sent to jail

Achievements.Name: Rolled To Freedom
Achievements.Description: Rolled a double to get out of jail

Achievements.Name: Globe Trotter
Achievements.Description: Land on every property on the World board

Achievements.Name: Taking Sides
Achievements.Description: Own every property, including any ports and utilities, down one whole side of the board

Achievements.Name: Transport King
Achievements.Description: Own the monopoly on the transport properties

Achievements.Name: You've Got The Power
Achievements.Description: Own the monopoly on the utilities

Achievements.Name: Deal Of The Century
Achievements.Description: Form a monopoly as a result of trading

Achievements.Name: No Mercy
Achievements.Description: Be responsible for the bankruptcy of another player

Achievements.Name: Went For Broke
Achievements.Description: Bankrupted yourself out of the game for the first time

Achievements.Name: A Good Start
Achievements.Description: Win your first mini-game in any mode of Richest

Achievements.Name: He Who Controls The Dice...
Achievements.Description: Win every mini-game in a full game of Developer

Achievements.Name: Last But Not Least
Achievements.Description: Win all the mini-games in a full game of Developer but don't finish first

Achievements.Name: Taken A Chance
Achievements.Description: Take your first property from another player using Chance in any mode of Richest

Achievements.Name: Forcibly Formed
Achievements.Description: Form a monopoly in any mode of Richest by taking one or more of the properties from another player.

Achievements.Name: Dashed Hopes
Achievements.Description: Break up another player's Monopoly

Achievements.Name: A Quick Victory
Achievements.Description: Win a game of Developer mode Richest

Achievements.Name: Faster Better
Achievements.Description: Win a game of Industrialist mode Richest

Achievements.Name: Becoming The Master
Achievements.Description: Win a game of Tycoon mode Richest

Achievements.Name: The Underdog
Achievements.Description: Don't finish first in any mini-game but still win overall in any mode of Richest

Achievements.Name: From The Flames
Achievements.Description: Come from last in the previous round to win overall in any mode of Richest

Achievements.Name: You Are The Richest
Achievements.Description: Own every property on the board in any mode of Richest

Achievements.Name: Started Your Empire
Achievements.Description: Build a set of houses in any mode of Richest

Achievements.Name: Established Your Hold
Achievements.Description: Build a set of hotels in any mode of Richest

Achievements.Name: Time To Collect
Achievements.Description: Collect your first rent payment from any other player in any mode of Richest

Achievements.Name: Expensive To Stop Here
Achievements.Description: Land on another player's set of hotels in any mode of Richest.

Achievements.Name: Sight Seer
Achievements.Description: Unlock a passport.  Awarded to the passport holder

Achievements.Name: Jet Setter
Achievements.Description: Fill all the passports.  Awarded to the passport holder

Achievements.Name: Try Something New
Achievements.Description: Unlock your first new board

Achievements.Name: The First MONOPOLY
Achievements.Description: Get the same amount of money as the year MONOPOLY was released
